PrecisEnactment of the DEFINITION OF "SMALL CABLE TRANSMISSION SYSTEM" REGULATIONS which define a "small cable transmission system" as one which transmits a signal to not more than 2,000 premises in the same licensed service area as set out by the Canadian Radio-Television and Telecommunications Commission.
